{"tid":1644060,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[極重要］黃色經濟","createTime":"2019-10-10T11:57:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T10:08:24.000Z","uid":210608,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c96065ccd986fcc0b53442ffc292e57f7dbf8cd5","tid":1644060,"uid":210608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T11:57:46.000Z","msg":"預計香港年尾經濟會差<br />\n會有人開始失業<br />\n不過，香港一直以來事實生左cancer<br />\n個cancer就係自由行同埋過份依賴中共經濟而被渣春袋<br />\n佢比商家搵快錢炒賣既機會<br />\n<br />\n對抗cancer係痛苦既，但痛苦只係短暫<br />\n痛苦過後係光復成功既香港<br />\n<br />\n手足開始製作藍黃食店攻略<br />\n我地唔只要10.10狂買黃店<br />\n係要每星期6，日都要，日日都要<br />\n仲要擴展都日常生活，唔剩只飲食，電話銀行交通所有野！<br />\n目的要淘汰藍店<br />\n<br />\n黃色經濟取代中共操抵的經濟<br />\n我地要自己渣番自己個春袋<br />\n<br />\n全民幫襯黃色經濟，撐起香港下半年<br />\n令黃色經濟成為bargining power<br />\n<br />\n真正光復香港🇭🇰時代革命"},{"pid":"597c5fc37a890679e32cc79987e213d9ec4a1179","tid":1644060,"uid":210608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:02:42.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"ef9b10963df4238f2382dd9e6ac06e823d7bc6fc","tid":1644060,"uid":135871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:03:03.000Z","msg":"［國際文宣］你地唔係唔記得呢單嘢啊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644067</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6897fa06466ec6d2478b2f282d072f003a19a2de","tid":1644060,"uid":254288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:04:04.000Z","msg":"支持黃色產業"},{"pid":"61f3e7aba78b7a8d94b11a1b93c56d881258c732","tid":1644060,"uid":210608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:07:34.000Z","msg":"tweet"},{"pid":"14447622566e851530dbe4d4794feed9be905514","tid":1644060,"uid":252973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:08:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b8da6b86204250f12c1cf1e1be0effcc801df0f","tid":1644060,"uid":54824,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T12:19:51.000Z","msg":"呢個名...."},{"pid":"6897f2307c4e4732284fff1ea